  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NeighbourSelection<Lecture,Placement>

    public class Suggestion
extends NeighbourSelectionWithSuggestions
    A simple neighbor selection based on NeighbourSelectionWithSuggestions, only triggering when there is an unassigned class. The selection picks a random unassigned class and tries to do a limited-depth search up to the Neighbour.SuggestionDepth depth. If successful, the returned suggestion is always considered improving as it finds an assignment that increases the number of assigned classes.
    Version:
    IFS 1.3 (Iterative Forward Search)
